data.description: If you build it, They will come! Perfect opportunity for a developer or an investor. 3.9 acre lot with 208 feet of Frontage on Fm 359. No restrictions so opportunity is Grand! Build a new subdivision or go Commercial/industrial. Semi/RV/boat storage, Business' Park, Commercial Retail the list goes on! Easy access to 1-10 and 1093. Location Is fantastic and is being developed quickly, surrounded by neighborhoods like Cross Creek West, Polo Ranch, Vanbrooke.
